    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm just jumping into Algolia InstantSearch. Really great so far!\r\n\r\nI'm looking to add keyboard navigation, specifically support for arrow keys and `enter` to select a result. Is there currently recommended way to add this to instantsearch results?",
